        "localization": {
          "name": "Great Narrative",
          "description": "This unit gains Stealth, a Stealth Shield and will Endure the next damage that would defeat it with 1HP. Endure effects cannot stack. Allies gain Spirit until ally Spirit reaches 8. These effects are triggered both at the very start of the battle if this unit is on the battlefield, and when this unit enters the battlefield from reinforcements.\n\nThis unit cannot be defeated by damage from Poison status effects.\n\nThis unit has a 100% chance to immediately have its TU reduced to 0 after the first time an ally is defeated while this unit is on the battlefield."
        }
      },
