          "description": "Allies gain 35% damage reduction from attacks while this unit is on the battlefield. This effect can stack with other damage reduction effects such as Armor, but will not stack with itself or other ally Barrier type skills.\n\nWhenever an ally takes damage from an attack, a random non-sleeping enemy becomes Mega Poisoned for 200TU. Mega Poison will overwrite other status effects on those enemies. Mega Poison deals 20 times the damage of normal Poison and cannot be overwritten by normal Poison or Super Poison."
